snippet.title: Season 02 Launch Trailer | Call of Duty: Modern Warfare II & Warzone 2.0
snippet.description:
The modern warrior always finds a way ⚔️

Resurgence on Ashika Island, MP Ranked Play, DMZ expansion, 1v1 Gulag, and so much more are coming to Season 02 free content update in Call of Duty #Warzone2 and #MWII on February 15th.

Follow #CallofDuty for the latest intel:
